# Security

- Store API keys and base URLs in Keychain; use kSecAttrAccessibleWhenUnlockedThisDeviceOnly
- Do not sync server credentials to iCloud
- Use ATS: NSAllowsLocalNetworking for self-hosted; add per-domain exceptions as needed
- Do not embed secrets in source or log credentials
